cast.overview: A married couple's life is turned upside down when the wife is accused of murdering her boss. Her husband John would spend the next few years trying to get her released, but there's no evidence that negates the evidence against her. When the strain of being separated from her husband and son gets to her, John decides to find a way to break her out.
cast.title: The Next Three Days

crew.overview: Tragedy strikes when a woman named Joyce's son falls through the ice on a frozen lake and is trapped underwater for over 15 minutes. After being rushed to the hospital, the 14-year-old boy continues to fight for his life as Joyce, her husband and their pastor stay by his bedside and pray for a miracle.
crew.title: Breakthrough

details.biography:
​From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia.

Tamara Gorski (born 21 November 1968) is a Canadian actress. She was born in Winnipeg, Manitoba, the daughter of a doctor.
